{
  "texts": [
    "• Novel Theoretical Framework for LLM Integration: A proposed theoretical framework is introduced to guide the ethical and effective integration of LLMs, such as ChatGPT, into educational systems.",
    "The framework provides actionable guidance by focusing on three interdependent pillars:o Personalized Learning Models: Offering tailored educational content to meet individual student needs through adaptive systems.",
    "o Ethical and Pedagogical Balance: Developing strategies to address challenges like AI bias, data privacy, and overreliance on AI, while enhancing critical thinking and human oversight.",
    "o Learning Adaptability Framework: Ensuring LLM flexibility across diverse educational contexts, such as K-12 classrooms, higher education, and online learning.• Systematic Review of LLMs: The article conducts a structured and comprehensive review of LLMs, including their history, training processes, and evaluation methods.",
    "This systematic review identifies underexplored areas in educational applications, such as the need for bias mitigation, privacy protections, and energy-efficient deployments."
  ]
}